      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Here's a roundup of the latest AI news today:\n\n## 🔥 Major Headlines\n\n### Musk vs. Altman / OpenAI Trial\n"
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The civil trial between the tech billionaires kicked off and could help define the future of artificial intelligence."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Musk claimed Altman betrayed the original principles of OpenAI to remain a nonprofit and that the company benefited from his money and connections."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n### AI & Defense\n"
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Google joins OpenAI in allowing the Pentagon to use its AI systems, as rival Anthropic remains embroiled in a court battle after seeking stronger safeguards."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The high-stakes conflict between the Defense Department and a $380 billion tech powerhouse goes to the heart of just how far AI can go in warfare."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n### AI Industry & Business\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "AI chipmaker Cerebras is said to target up to $4 billion in its IPO."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Apple raised the Mac Mini's starting price to $799 after AI frenzy drains supply."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Meta acquired a robotics AI company to help build humanoid technology."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Alphabet broke away with a 63% surge in Google Cloud revenue to US$20 billion for Q1 2026."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n### AI Infrastructure & Cloud\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Amazon Connect Talent — now available in preview — uses AI \"teammates\" to conduct 24/7 interviews and score candidates."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "A bill that had passed both chambers of a state legislature would have imposed the country's first statewide moratorium on new data center construction."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n### AI Policy & Regulation\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "A governor is emerging as a voice of AI skepticism in the Republican Party, but state lawmakers declined to take up the push for legislation."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Many companies are increasingly looking to AI agents as a way to boost employee productivity and automate rote chores."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n### AI Research\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "MIT released a new dataset of 30,000-plus competition math problems from 47 countries, giving AI researchers a harder test and students worldwide a better training ground."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "A new training method improves the reliability of AI confidence estimates without sacrificing performance, addressing a root cause of hallucination in reasoning models."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "A new lab from MIT and IBM will chart the convergence of AI, algorithms, and quantum computing."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n### AI Model Releases\n"
      },
      {
